article.headline: Texas State 106, Dallas Baptist 93
article.story: SAN MARCOS, Texas (AP) -- Brandon Bush scored 27 points to lead Texas State to a 106-93 win over Dallas Baptist on Friday night in the season opener for both teams. Also scoring in double digits for Texas State were Charles Dotson with 18, Matt Fullenwider with 13 and Chris Agwumaro with 12. Bush shot 10-of-15 from the field. Nick Michels led Dallas Baptist with 29 points. Also scoring in double-digits were Dwight Coleman and Jonathan Teat with 10 points each. At the half, Texas State led 57-34.
